                    <p><strong>Čo t&yacute;m z&iacute;skate:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>stretnete veľa inteligentn&yacute;ch, zauj&iacute;mav&yacute;ch ľud&iacute; z&nbsp;r&ocirc;znych odvetv&iacute;;</li>
